refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns a deflate context resource (zlib.deflate) on
 success, &return.falseforfailure;.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    8.0.0

     On success, this function returns a DeflateContext instance now;
     previously, a resource was returned.
